    <detaileddescription>
<para>object of this struct can be passed to range-based-for to enumerate all entries in a filesystem directory <emphasis>including</emphasis> all subdirectories and <emphasis>without</emphasis> throwing exceptions e.g. std::error_code ec; for ( auto dirEntry : <ref refid="structMR_1_1DirectoryRecursive" kindref="compound">DirectoryRecursive</ref>{ std::filesystem::current_path(), ec } ) { ... } </para>
